OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:
OL,6,FStaying hot, sunny and mostly dry over
OL,7,Fthe next few days with temperatures
OL,8,Fwell above average. A little more
OL,9,Fpatchy cloud on Thursday, perhaps with
OL,10,Fthe odd shower.
